---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <section slot="head">
    <title>Inmocredit - Tu camino hacia el hogar propio</title>
  </section>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative w-full bg-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-max-width mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop py-xl grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-lg items-center">
      <div class="z-10">
        <h1 class="font-headline-xl text-headline-xl text-deep-blue mb-md leading-tight">
          El camino hacia tu tranquilidad comienza aquí.
        </h1>
        <p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-lg max-w-lg">
          Simplificamos el proceso de crédito, reduciendo trámites y papeleo, para que te enfoques en lo más importante: tu bienestar y el de tu familia.
        </p>
        <a href="/servicios" class="inline-block bg-[#FF6B35] text-white font-label-md text-label-md px-lg py-md rounded-lg shadow-lg shadow-primary-container/20 hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform active:scale-95">
          VER SERVICIOS
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="relative h-[400px] md:h-[600px] rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
        <img
          alt="Modern House"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/30652918/pexels-photo-30652918.jpeg"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ¿Por qué elegirnos? Section -->
  <section class="bg-crema py-xl">
    <div class="max-w-max-width mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop text-center">
      <h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-deep-blue mb-xl">¿Por qué elegirnos?</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-gutter">
        <div class="bg-white p-lg rounded-xl shadow-soft border border-outline-variant hover:border-secondary transition-colors group">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-secondary-container/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-md">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-[40px]">verified_user</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-deep-blue mb-sm">Confiable</h3>
          <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
Asesoría profesional y acompañamiento transparente en cada paso de tu financiamiento.

          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-lg rounded-xl shadow-soft border border-outline-variant hover:border-secondary transition-colors group">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-secondary-container/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-md">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-[40px]">bolt</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-deep-blue mb-sm">Rápido</h3>
          <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
            Procesos ágiles y respuestas rápidas para que obtengas tu crédito sobre propiedad en el menor tiempo posible.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-lg rounded-xl shadow-soft border border-outline-variant hover:border-secondary transition-colors group">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-secondary-container/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-md">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-[40px]">payments</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-deep-blue mb-sm">Seguro</h3>
          <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
            Protegemos tu información y gestionamos tu crédito con total respaldo y confianza.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Nuestros Pilares Section -->
  <section class="bg-white py-xl overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-max-width mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-xl items-center">
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
          <div class="inline-block px-sm py-xs bg-primary-fixed text-primary rounded-full font-label-md text-label-md mb-md">
            NUESTRA ESENCIA
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-deep-blue mb-lg">Nuestros pilares</h2>
          <div class="space-y-md">
            <div class="flex gap-md">
              <div class="mt-1 text-primary">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined">home</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-headline-md text-[20px] text-deep-blue">Construimos patrimonio</h4>
                <p class="text-on-surface-variant">Más que financiamiento, ayudamos a crear estabilidad y oportunidades de crecimiento.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-md">
              <div class="mt-1 text-primary">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined">handshake</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-headline-md text-[20px] text-deep-blue">Relaciones de confianza</h4>
                <p class="text-on-surface-variant">Creemos en relaciones transparentes y duraderas con cada cliente.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-md">
              <div class="mt-1 text-primary">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined">rocket_launch</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-headline-md text-[20px] text-deep-blue">Soluciones que avanzan contigo</h4>
                <p class="text-on-surface-variant">Nos adaptamos a las necesidades actuales del mercado para ofrecer alternativas rápidas y confiables.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 grid grid-cols-2 gap-md">
          <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden h-64 shadow-lg">
            <img
              alt="Pillar 1"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDDOjHTN9pYxIZGRyp7MkhPu8mx_TLVAqXP0_KDhdo1wLHvxn-rev1q9Pr3RbJe_AVObAccOnmcAEupBayXPNucWc-FMiaSxt9bMZm2wcGatvEEfCdbFDjpNbEtdmq9pd8fjgr3za2m8wNFYGnG68YbWGbzye_MGFwjckGjcdOsIRlOgywAY7m2o3vDwLl_N96oJv-76eCl8G2SrA63AzNv92qHqU1pWk-4VFSJc6mvhVlNK619SKNoE3w4Od8NDHgh9lIiqn4LI14"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden h-64 mt-lg shadow-lg">
            <img
              alt="Pillar 2"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAxJL7w-bYxsdM_Sv-6hvmEEc8n_vAD1x1hZLey9noVtRm86HYSqU_GNhNaPsChP6EY5m_CwzdxFF_AMupn1m68SLoG6NH8vFS_hDeacGq_t0gBo36R2lsR9bWLJe7MZJs6NEpN68P0QT2-QuTM6PukkSiuVJntLpKyEOFHZ7K0eZNAyNfP-mmUwtJHjoVLsqTfTEq3_7FelpBhXXCqUq_RtIrTu_IfzwZAsAGHlBA7QEc7-X_pxgxP5YZNW4G604HKRlzE8qmaDYs"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Strip -->
  <div class="bg-surface-container-low py-lg border-y border-outline-variant">
    <div class="max-w-max-width mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-md">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-md">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-[32px]">phone_in_talk</span>
        <div>
          <p class="font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface-variant uppercase">Llámanos directamente</p>
          <p class="font-headline-md text-deep-blue">+502 5094-8707</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hidden md:block w-px h-12 bg-outline-variant"></div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-md">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-[32px]">apartment</span>
        <div>
          <p class="font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface-variant uppercase">PBX Central</p>
          <p class="font-headline-md text-deep-blue">+502 2354-6196</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a href="/contacto" class="bg-primary text-on-primary px-lg py-md rounded-full font-label-md text-label-md hover:bg-on-primary-fixed-variant transition-colors">
        CONTÁCTANOS
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
